    "description": "<strong>帮助阿米莉亚踏上文艺复兴时期的旅程，进入梦幻般的奇异世界！</strong><br>收集资源，建造塔楼，抵御一波又一波的伊丽莎白·巴托里[/b]助手。<br>面对一群想要帮助贵族实施邪恶计划的狂热分子。解放你的同学，利用他们的帮助来摆脱这个麻烦的梦想。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252360/extras/22510d9ce89e53b1e6dcea986b5740b0.poster.avif?t=1728899612\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252360/extras/22510d9ce89e53b1e6dcea986b5740b0.webm?t=1728899612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252360/extras/22510d9ce89e53b1e6dcea986b5740b0.mp4?t=1728899612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >经典塔防</h2></strong> 哪里有塔楼，哪里就一定有一波又一波的敌人！你会遇到一位血腥的伯爵夫人，她在途中创造了历史！这个梦幻般的世界充满了奇怪而扭曲的生物，它们是她的爪牙。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252360/extras/3f99d53624d9c3df2b94b7cd89983fb0.poster.avif?t=1728899612\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252360/extras/3f99d53624d9c3df2b94b7cd89983fb0.webm?t=1728899612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252360/extras/3f99d53624d9c3df2b94b7cd89983fb0.mp4?t=1728899612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >塔楼、升级和仆从</h2></strong> 收集木材和石头等资源来建造和升级防御塔。除了弹弓之外，它们将是你对抗对手的主要防御。在战斗中使用你的助手，为他们分配简单的任务并保卫你的蜘蛛基地 - 贾维斯！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252360/extras/2e03688c39f7399a34b94ba73eecb5f2.poster.avif?t=1728899612\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252360/extras/2e03688c39f7399a34b94ba73eecb5f2.webm?t=1728899612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252360/extras/2e03688c39f7399a34b94ba73eecb5f2.mp4?t=1728899612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >合作和单人游戏模式</h2></strong> 在这个疯狂的世界中，无论是独自一人还是在分屏合作模式下与一群最好的朋友一起踏上这场奇妙的冒险。",
